1 to 1 Math classes is all about developing love for the world of Mathematics.  This is done by Learning by Doing. There are no theoretical lectures. Concepts are introduced using physical tools. Students manipulate these tools and discover the concept. Once they start understanding, books are introduced where they apply their understanding in solving the problems. This lays the strong foundation of Mathematics. Students are able to relate with their everyday life and retain the concept forever.
EDUCATORS
Our dedicated educators craft tailored lessons that create curiosity and critical thinking in a child’s mind. We inspire our students to explore the wonders of mathematics by introducing them to new ideas of learning and exploring. Our teachers use activity-based methods to make learning fun and easy. This is the reason we call our teacher Facilitators. They do not teach, but they facilitate activities in the way that students are able to discover concepts. With our personalised attention and engaging lessons, we help